Package com.example.app.components.appnav

Class AppNav

java.lang.Object
com.vaadin.flow.component.Component
com.example.app.components.appnav.AppNav
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.vaadin.flow.component.AttachNotifier, com.vaadin.flow.component.DetachNotifier, com.vaadin.flow.component.HasElement, com.vaadin.flow.component.HasSize, com.vaadin.flow.component.HasStyle, Serializable
@JsModule("@vaadin-component-factory/vcf-nav") @Tag("vcf-nav") public class AppNav extends com.vaadin.flow.component.Component implements com.vaadin.flow.component.HasSize, com.vaadin.flow.component.HasStyle
A navigation menu with support for hierarchical and flat menus.

Items can be added using #addItem(AppNavItem) and hierarchy can be created by adding AppNavItem instances to other AppNavItem instances.
